com.splunk
Class AtomObject

java.lang.Object
  com.splunk.AtomObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
AtomEntry, AtomFeed
public class AtomObject
extends java.lang.Object

The AtomObject class represents a generic Atom object. This is a common base class shared by AtomFeed and AtomEntry.
